'''鲁大维''' （{{lang-en|David M. Robinson}}, {{bd|1965年|5月27日||}}）是一位美国汉学家。中文名叫'''鲁大维'''。

==生平==
毕业于[[霍巴特和威廉史密斯学院|霍巴特和威廉史密斯学院]]和[[普林斯顿大学|普林斯顿大学]]，<ref>{{cite news |title=David Robinson |url=http://www.colgate.edu/facultysearch/FacultyDirectory/david-robinson |accessdate=May 30, 2018 |publisher=Colgate University}}</ref>任教于[[柯盖德大学|柯盖德大学]]。<ref>{{cite book |title=Empire’s Twilight |date=December 2009 |publisher=Harvard University Press |isbn=9780674036086 |url=http://www.hup.harvard.edu/catalog.php?isbn=9780674036086&content=bios}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Dr. David M. Robinson, Robert H.N. Ho Professor in Asian Studies, Professor of History, Colgate University - "Empire's Shadow: The Ming Court in Eurasia |url=https://ceas.sas.upenn.edu/events/dr-david-m-robinson-robert-hn-ho-professor-asian-studies-professor-history-colgate-university |accessdate=May 30, 2018 |publisher=University of Pennsylvania |date=February 2014}}</ref>主要研究[[蒙古帝国|蒙古帝国]]和[[明朝|明朝]]历史。

